Global COB Encapsulant Market Insights
COB Encapsulant Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12% from 2024 to 2030.

COB Encapsulant Market Overview
The global COB Encapsulant Market was valued at USD 4.67 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach USD 8.11 billion by 2030, with a CAGR of 7.8% during the forecast period. The market is driven by the increasing demand for high-performance LED lighting solutions, as well as advancements in the packaging technologies for LEDs. The COB (Chip-on-Board) technology is becoming increasingly popular in various applications such as automotive lighting, signage, and display systems, contributing to the market’s growth. The growing need for energy-efficient lighting solutions and miniaturization in electronic devices further drive demand for COB encapsulants across diverse sectors.

